data.description: Introducing a charming and rustic 4-bedroom, 2-bath cabin-style home, nestled amidst the tranquility of nature. This enchanting property offers the perfect blend of rustic charm and modern comfort, making it an idyllic retreat for those seeking a serene escape from the hustle and bustle of city life.Step inside, and you'll find a spacious and open floor plan with vaulted ceilings that emphasize the cabin's airy and welcoming atmosphere. The living room boasts a stone fireplace that stretches to the ceiling, providing both warmth and a focal point for cozy evenings by the fire. This cabin boasts four comfortable bedrooms, each thoughtfully designed to provide a restful sanctuary for its occupants. The primary suite, located on the main floor, offers convenience and privacy. Located conveniently near schools, parks, and shopping, this property has it all. Don't miss this opportunity to make it your forever home!
